nodes.text: DS-378 was a stormtrooper who conducted operations as part of Imperial Security for the Galactic Empire's Quarantine Zone on the planet Dathomir during the time of the Galactic Civil War.

DS-378 was first mentioned in the 2003 video game Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided, a massively multiplayer online role-playing game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
